title: >>> RUMORS Welcome
body_text:
--- It has been a long time since the last "RUMORS Welcome" page. It's about time to bring it back!
I.
Derek Carty asked to be put on this week's poster.
II.
Like last week, captains have yet to be decided.
III.
Diana DiBuccio underwent surgery this week to repair her broken right pinky finger.
IV.
Both Winston sisters are currently dating two Adams brothers.
V.
Mike "Sputz" will be returning at DODGEBALL LVI after missing DODGEBALL FIFTY-FIVE.
VI.
Kevin Megill refused to make an "opponent alliance" with John Tronolone this past event [if they managed to be on seperate teams].
--- A short, simple, yet unpredictable post here on the dodgeball website. The writer looks forward to your attendance at DODGEBALL LVI!
